# DISABLED PLACEHOLDER — DO NOT LOAD

This file uses underscore prefix + `.disabled` suffix and is **not loaded** by the planner.
It exists only to mark where the future PR B (general-tech-qa narrow path) will live.

Loader rules:
- `embed.FS` glob is `capabilities/*.md` (no `.disabled`)
- Files with leading underscore are skipped even if matching glob

If you see this loaded by the planner, the loader is broken. File an issue.

PR B will live in `general_tech_qa.md` (no underscore, no `.disabled`) and be wired in a separate PR after PR A merges.
